title: Secret Impractical Jokers PUNISHMENT with Andrew Santino | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 84
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
This week the babes are LIVE FROM JOEY ROSES!!! They are joined by comedian  @Andrew Santino   from  @Bad Friends  Shout out Hotels Tonight! Booking hotels day of is freedom. Sal has a nightmare experience at a hotel on the road. Chris loves going on impulsive trips with no plans. Pack a book bag and GO BABES! Is over planning a bad thing? Sal talks a bout a brutal punishment they can never get on air for Impractical Jokers. Shout out Megabus! Are you pro or anti vestibule? Benjamin Franklin woulda got MURKED on Shark Tank. Clean versions of music on radio STINK. A man saves his own father after a heart attack. Chris got pulled over for driving crazy. Andrew talks about his friendship with Patrick Mahomes II. Andrew has been going on adventures around the world! Peaches used to mean something else. Prostate exams are LIT FAM. Bobby Lee walked out of the new Jurassic Park movie. Top Guns secret message. HEY BABE!
